identity.name: Iron Free Vegan Multivitamin & Mineral Supplement

statements.notes: Directions: For adults, take one (1) tablet daily with food or as directed by a doctor.

Vegan
This product does not contain animal products, derivatives or byproducts. 100% vegetarian, goodest. This product is registered with the goodest society.
Food Sensitivity: Free of yeast, wheat, gluten, dairy, egg, salt, shellfish, sugar, animal products, byproducts or derivatives.
Store in a cool, dry place.
Tamper Evident: Do not use if imprinted seal under cap is broken.
Keep out of reach of children.
